Tamurt n '''Spanya''' d amaslaḍ di Tidukkli n Tmura n Turuft (UE). Tezga-d seg unzulataram n [[Turuft]] akked deg [[Tefriqt Ugafa]]. 
Tamanaɣt-is d [[Madrid]].<br/>
Deg aneẓaw n turuft tḥerr amur ameqran seg tazunegzirt n [[Iberia]]. Ama deg tefriqt ugafa, tesɛa snat n timdinin deg wakal  n umeṛṛuk [[Sebta]]
akked [[Mlilt]].<br/>
Deg [[Ilel Agrakal]] tesɛa Tigzirin Balears. Ama deg ugaraw aṭlantik tesɛa Tigzirin Tiknariyin. <br/>
Ɣef leḥsab n tmenḍawt n Spanya deg amagrad wis 3.1 n usaḍuf, [[Taspanyulit]]  '''el castellano''' d tutalyt tunṣibt n uwanak.

